# Load R Models from Unity Catalog

While `{mlflow}` doesn't support directly logging R models to Unity Catalog, you can actually load models without much trouble.

## How to Load Models from Unity Catalog

::: callout-note
Thankfully its usually smooth sailing once the model is registered to Unity Catalog
:::






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
mlflow_load_model("models:/zacdav.default.my_simple_r_model@champ")
```
:::






Yep, much more straightforward than getting the R model there in the first place.
